    "id": "5747",
    "title": "Víctimas de los bombardeos en Mallorca sin memoria",
    "url": "https://manuelaguilerapovedano.wordpress.com/2025/09/26/victimas-de-los-bombardeos-en-mallorca-sin-memoria/",
    "date": "septiembre 26, 2025",
    "categoria": "historia",
    "content": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">\n                                El pueblo de Artà (Mallorca) colocará piedras de la memoria con las víctimas del\n                                bombardeo fascista italiano de 1936. El resto de víctimas de los bombardeos de Mallorca\n                                <strong> nunca ha tenido memoria\n                                </strong>\n                                .\n                            </p>\n                            <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">\n                                Programa Al Dia de IB3 Televisión del 26 de septiembre de 2025.\n                            </p>\n                            <figure\n                                class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\">\n                                <div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n                                    <span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"> <iframe\n                                            class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\"\n                                            src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/PooGP8lMuGg?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=es&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\"\n                                            allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\"\n                                            sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\">\n                                        </iframe>\n                                    </span>\n                                </div>\n                            </figure>\n                        </div>"
