    "id": "5603",
    "title": "Encontrados los familiares de Amador Herrero Torres",
    "url": "https://manuelaguilerapovedano.wordpress.com/2024/10/21/buscamos-familiares-de-amador-herrero-torres/",
    "date": "octubre 21, 2024",
    "categoria": "historia",
    "content": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">\n                                Hemos encontrado a los familiares del miliciano\n                                <strong> AMADOR HERRERO TORRES\n                                </strong>\n                                . Muchas gracias a las personas que nos habéis ayudado.\n                            </p>\n                            <div\n                                class=\"wp-block-group is-vertical is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-4fc3f8e1 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n                                <div\n                                    class=\"wp-block-group is-vertical is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-4fc3f8e1 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n                                    <div class=\"wp-block-group\">\n                                        <div\n                                            class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n                                            <ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n                                                <li>\n                                                    Miliciano de UGT\n                                                </li>\n                                                <li>\n                                                    Casado con\n                                                    <strong> Josefa Terol Bas\n                                                    </strong>\n                                                </li>\n                                                <li>\n                                                    Padre de cinco hijos\n                                                </li>\n                                                <li>\n                                                    Asesinado en 1936 en Mallorca\n                                                </li>\n                                                <li>\n                                                    33 años\n                                                </li>\n                                                <li>\n                                                    De\n                                                    <strong> Jumilla\n                                                    </strong>\n                                                    (Murcia)\n                                                </li>\n                                                <li>\n                                                    Residente en\n                                                    <strong> Manresa\n                                                    </strong>\n                                                    (BCN)\n                                                </li>\n                                            </ul>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                            <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">\n                                Contacto: manuelaguilerapovedano@gmail.com\n                            </p>\n                            <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">\n                                <a href=\"https://www.ultimahora.es/opinion/tribuna/2024/10/12/2257727/amador-herrero-torres-miliciano-desconocido.html\"\n                                    target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"> Aquí su historia publicada en el diario\n                                    Ultima Hora (Mallorca)\n                                </a>\n                            </p>\n                            <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">\n                            </p>\n                            <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n                                <a\n                                    href=\"https://manuelaguilerapovedano.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/amador-herrero-torres.-miliciano-bayo-mallorca.jpeg\">\n                                    <img data-attachment-id=\"5607\"\n                                        data-permalink=\"https://manuelaguilerapovedano.wordpress.com/2024/10/21/buscamos-familiares-de-amador-herrero-torres/amador-herrero-torres-miliciano-bayo-mallorca/\"\n                                        data-orig-file=\"https://manuelaguilerapovedano.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/amador-herrero-torres.-miliciano-bayo-mallorca.jpeg\"\n                                        data-orig-size=\"900,675\" data-comments-opened=\"1\"\n                                        data-image-meta=\"{&#34;aperture&#34;:&#34;0&#34;,&#34;credit&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;camera&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;caption&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;created_timestamp&#34;:&#34;0&#34;,&#34;copyright&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;focal_length&#34;:&#34;0&#34;,&#34;iso&#34;:&#34;0&#34;,&#34;shutter_speed&#34;:&#34;0&#34;,&#34;title&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;orientation&#34;:&#34;0&#34;}\"\n                                        data-image-title=\"Amador Herrero Torres. Miliciano Bayo Mallorca\"\n                                        data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\"\n                                        data-large-file=\"https://manuelaguilerapovedano.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/amador-herrero-torres.-miliciano-bayo-mallorca.jpeg?w=640\"\n                                        loading=\"lazy\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\"\n                                        src=\"https://manuelaguilerapovedano.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/amador-herrero-torres.-miliciano-bayo-mallorca.jpeg?w=900\"\n                                        alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-5607\"\n                                        srcset=\"https://manuelaguilerapovedano.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/amador-herrero-torres.-miliciano-bayo-mallorca.jpeg 900w, https://manuelaguilerapovedano.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/amador-herrero-torres.-miliciano-bayo-mallorca.jpeg?w=150 150w, https://manuelaguilerapovedano.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/amador-herrero-torres.-miliciano-bayo-mallorca.jpeg?w=300 300w, https://manuelaguilerapovedano.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/amador-herrero-torres.-miliciano-bayo-mallorca.jpeg?w=768 768w\"\n                                        sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" />\n                                </a>\n                            </figure>\n                        </div>"
