    "id": "5448",
    "title": "Audiolibro de ‘El oro de Mussolini’",
    "url": "https://manuelaguilerapovedano.wordpress.com/2023/12/04/audiolibro-de-el-oro-de-mussolini/",
    "date": "diciembre 4, 2023",
    "categoria": "academico",
    "content": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">\n                                Ya está disponible el audiolibro de\n                                <em> El oro de Mussolini\n                                </em>\n                                .\n                            </p>\n                            <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">\n                                Narrado por el actor Joel Valverde ‼️🔝\n                            </p>\n                            <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">\n                                Os animo a escuchar el inicio:\n                                <a\n                                    href=\"https://www.storytel.com/mx/books/el-oro-de-mussolini-mussolinis-gold-c%C3%B3mo-la-rep%C3%BAblica-plane%C3%B3-vender-parte-de-espa%C3%B1a-al-fascismo-2725713\">\n                                    Storytel\n                                </a>\n                                –\n                                <a\n                                    href=\"https://play.google.com/store/audiobooks/details?id=AQAAAEASajgqOM&amp;gl=GB&amp;hl=en-GB&amp;source=productsearch&amp;pcampaignid=MKT-DR-na-us-1000189-Med-hasem-bk-Evergreen-Nov1417-PLA-audiobookspla*AQAAAEASajgqOM\">\n                                    Google Play audiolibro\n                                </a>\n                                –\n                                <a\n                                    href=\"https://www.amazon.es/El-oro-Mussolini-Rep%C3%BAblica-Fascismo/dp/B0CP4F6P91/ref=tmm_aud_swatch_0?_encoding=UTF8&amp;qid=&amp;sr=\">\n                                    Amazon audiolibro\n                                </a>\n                            </p>\n                            <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n                                <a\n                                    href=\"https://manuelaguilerapovedano.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/cubierta_oro_mussolini_final_3edic.jpg\">\n                                    <img data-attachment-id=\"4603\"\n                                        data-permalink=\"https://manuelaguilerapovedano.wordpress.com/2022/07/21/el-oro-de-mussolini-entre-los-mas-vendidos-de-historia/cubierta_oro_mussolini_final_3edic/\"\n                                        data-orig-file=\"https://manuelaguilerapovedano.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/cubierta_oro_mussolini_final_3edic.jpg\"\n                                        data-orig-size=\"2094,3169\" data-comments-opened=\"1\"\n                                        data-image-meta=\"{&#34;aperture&#34;:&#34;0&#34;,&#34;credit&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;camera&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;caption&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;created_timestamp&#34;:&#34;0&#34;,&#34;copyright&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;focal_length&#34;:&#34;0&#34;,&#34;iso&#34;:&#34;0&#34;,&#34;shutter_speed&#34;:&#34;0&#34;,&#34;title&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;orientation&#34;:&#34;0&#34;}\"\n                                        data-image-title=\"cubierta_oro_mussolini_final_3edic\" data-image-description=\"\"\n                                        data-image-caption=\"\"\n                                        data-large-file=\"https://manuelaguilerapovedano.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/cubierta_oro_mussolini_final_3edic.jpg?w=640\"\n                                        loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"968\"\n                                        src=\"https://manuelaguilerapovedano.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/cubierta_oro_mussolini_final_3edic.jpg?w=640\"\n                                        alt=\"Portada de El oro de Mussolini\" class=\"wp-image-4603\"\n                                        srcset=\"https://manuelaguilerapovedano.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/cubierta_oro_mussolini_final_3edic.jpg?w=640 640w, https://manuelaguilerapovedano.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/cubierta_oro_mussolini_final_3edic.jpg?w=1280 1280w, https://manuelaguilerapovedano.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/cubierta_oro_mussolini_final_3edic.jpg?w=99 99w, https://manuelaguilerapovedano.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/cubierta_oro_mussolini_final_3edic.jpg?w=198 198w, https://manuelaguilerapovedano.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/cubierta_oro_mussolini_final_3edic.jpg?w=768 768w, https://manuelaguilerapovedano.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/cubierta_oro_mussolini_final_3edic.jpg?w=677 677w\"\n                                        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" />\n                                </a>\n                            </figure>\n                        </div>"
